{"tid":83470,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"諗唔到標題呀，喫屎啦。","createTime":"2017-01-16T18:15:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T05:29:36.000Z","uid":9290,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cd31a823d86baf9bfb715cba235ae6062307b9db","tid":83470,"uid":9290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T18:15:07.000Z","msg":"人天生都不可以愛死身邊的一個呀！<br />\n<br />\n喺架，可能真喺唔可以架，未來嘅野有邊個可以拍曬心口保證<br />\n口講一生一世，又有幾多真喺做到？<br />\n但我願意試 我願意為你試<br />\n<br />\n喺，人喺自私，我愛你都喺因為我自私<br />\n我想擁有你，我好想努力捉緊你<br />\n但我唔知會有啲咩反後果<br />\n所以我努力配合緊你 俾自由你<br />\n<br />\n我有缺點，我願意改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔去咁依賴，搵野俾自己做<br />\n我只係想好好咁愛你，你明唔明？<br />\n<br />\n屌估唔到要喺5P台開POST，我唔開心都冇話你知<br />\n你會唔會睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ea1d21e172aa2e7ad090d4d12ba2d7574fc3fc2","tid":83470,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T18:17:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc02e78079095eb2acc06d966dfb76f45a3d2c7f","tid":83470,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T18:27:07.000Z","msg":"喺乜春呀戇鳩"},{"pid":"a35f82d4463c50d21107a9d2d099f5c244d6da07","tid":83470,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T18:28:32.000Z","msg":"瞓唔着<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe393dffe01be952294d6057b9b8f13ccc86e44","tid":83470,"uid":27770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T18:29:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbacd28fb2adab0ce518f514d7d0c0717e75ee33","tid":83470,"uid":9290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T01:59:32.000Z","msg":"瞓唔著之餘仲要好早醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb7ad966cb78b4c8b980400cdde6e2e84120b9d","tid":83470,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s